{"status":200,"code":1000,"message":null,"timestamp":"1762168715025","path":null,"data":{"id":1466,"title":"AIA:「癌症全方位保障3」系列計劃轉換安排","type":"PRODUCT_NEWS","time":1672019201337,"tags":["友邦保險"],"content":"<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">致合作夥伴：</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>友邦</strong>將為所有持有<strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">「癌症全方位保障」系列及「癌症全方位保障2」系列</span></strong>保單的合資格客戶<span style=\"color: #236fa1;\"><strong>提供一次性計劃轉換安排</strong></span>，透過簡單健康聲明<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong>將上述系列產品</strong></span>轉換至相同或較低計劃級別的<strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">「癌症全方位保障3」系列</span></strong>。假如客戶錯過此一次性安排，友邦亦提供一般安排，客戶可透過進行健康核保申請計劃轉換。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; A.一次性計劃轉換特別安排</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1）計劃轉換時間表</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/2022-12-25/5e2e5a7145ea4d4fbee946e72da69207.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2）適用之計劃轉換種類</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-righ